:''note, this etymology is distinct from the etymology of [[wise]]''

===Noun===
'''wiseacre'''
# one who [[feign]]s knowledge or [[clever]]ness; an [[insolent]] [[upstart]]

===Synonyms===
* [[smart aleck]]
* [[smarty]] ''or'' [[smartie]]
